</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65333045"><p>We need to seriously think about at least mirroring stuff like Wikipedia and maybe the Internet Archive outside the US. Ideally in multiple different countries on different continents.</p><p>It's no small task but things can go bad, anywhere.</p></div>
	</div>

